<subSubSection pageId="53" pageNumber="537" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="53.[1402,2612,272,859]" pageId="53" pageNumber="537">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1404,1762,706,739]" pageId="53" pageNumber="537">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Uncertain taxonomic status of Hernandez’s Short-tailed Bat makes a conservation assessment difficult.
